------------------------------------------
Scene Switcher – Fast Scene Navigation
------------------------------------------

Thank you for downloading Scene Switcher Pro!

This tool helps you switch between Unity scenes quickly and easily.
No more hunting through folders — just one click and you’re there.

------------------------------------------
FEATURES
------------------------------------------
- One-click scene switching
- Tabs for Build Settings & All Scenes
- Auto-refresh scene lists
- Toggle for save prompt (juicy and colorful)
- Locate button (ping scene in Project window)
- Welcome window with quick-start guide

------------------------------------------
INSTALLATION
------------------------------------------
1. Import the package into your Unity project.
2. Go to the menu: Tools > Scene Switcher.
3. Start switching scenes instantly.

------------------------------------------
USAGE
------------------------------------------
- Click a scene button to switch directly.
- Use the locate button (small icon) to highlight the scene in Project view.
- Control auto-save prompts with the toggle.
- Tabs help you manage Build Settings vs All Scenes.

